<paragraph id="64745BE07E8F01727D8C09D3B9C41113" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Kleine Kronwicke</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="B9F3C5752169CDF945E0BBBD04D69FD8" pageId="null" pageNumber="554" type="description">
<paragraph id="AE5CA3C3431274DDB8D913CB8247F2FB" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="5431051A76C2B275E5692F7A04AA674F" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Coronilla" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="554" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vaginalis">
<emphasis id="F5F34020CB0708D961EA1B02333AC5B7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">C. vaginalis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 3) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="7F33FCAD72BF3BB2B0FC828E97865569" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
<normalizedToken id="898E0B7F1E5AF94A05A3201630107CDB" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
ungestielt; 
<normalizedToken id="CC155BE342F079BC61B1C516E2D9176F" originalValue="Nebenblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Nebenblaetter</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
⅓- 
<normalizedToken id="4EA660BD01C54985A0BCC5A3B4509625" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="8E484083406228E5413AF8B1182CB9EE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
so lang wie die untersten 
<normalizedToken id="B2913E1EC64EE5BAA47B77710B193678" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
; Krone 0,5-0,8 cm lang;
</emphasis>
Frucht 1,5-2,5 cm lang; Glieder der Frucht mit 4 stumpfen Kanten, nicht 
<normalizedToken id="0F9DE2C8E30559D60D98C423E53CD46E" originalValue="geflügelt" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">gefluegelt</normalizedToken>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="732A934533D643EFDEA106CDFF08BA9B" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="26CD652E9EA385AB72839CA052DD5D70" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="246F3B0F7BC36D75798E4D083F6634BD" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B56D689E36771709ED8515B86FBBBFBB" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
<emphasis id="9814625060B899EB8999A515B7B08FB7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="D25A45FF544CB14031CC48EC63E709DE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">12:</emphasis>
Material aus den 
<normalizedToken id="8C045C7A0062C4B8DC934D4B1675511B" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="A59A0E297033BE7260AE85E2CA4350FC" originalValue="Küpfer" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Kuepfer</normalizedToken>
1969). 
<emphasis id="44DF271FEC59E61B00900252007E3301" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="3AACB14255D70DB3ABDFBC416CB09FE1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">24:</emphasis>
Material aus 
<normalizedToken id="F9631D637F1AB8A8B6CF642AAD580E99" originalValue="Südfrankreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Suedfrankreich</normalizedToken>
(Caussols) (Guinochet und Logeois 1962).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CE54EE78D4558A3C3662502DC0240B55" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
<emphasis id="33D29C449A0B346247E7F660EA25D084" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
<pageBreakToken id="5CD1ED2365B1549549264A69BD89C4B2" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Standort</pageBreakToken>
.
</emphasis>
Kollin, selten montan. Trockene, sandige, kalkhaltige 
<normalizedToken id="8E4398D0399F28436E1FCC5CBFCC6FEA" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Lichte 
<normalizedToken id="7591A04ADAE2C6CE3058151FF46B43C4" originalValue="Föhrenwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Foehrenwaelder</normalizedToken>
, Felsensteppen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6EED693E8C839B56CAFD32DF3974215E" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">
<emphasis id="9951558D59692CB156723649F48DE0E7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Verbreitung. Westmediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="A96641E57AE5DE511D08E79C08573E7B" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="A7B610703785390171F2B8BF6B39786E" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Normandie, Lothringen, Wallis, 
<normalizedToken id="29D2271ECAD076B0AABCAFF801ED9B50" originalValue="Südtirol" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Suedtirol</normalizedToken>
, Apenninenhalbinsel; Nordwestafrika. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel et al. (1965). - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="2158930E83F380B8DACB34EA917AF049" originalValue="Südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura, Savoyen, 
<normalizedToken id="0F0755084E954C5897B85FF0B5604287" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain, Gegend von 
<normalizedToken id="4340352C4648854D5C8BAA16C81DB8F2" originalValue="Chambéry" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Chambery</normalizedToken>
, Maurienne, Mittelwallis (Siders bis Guttet), Aostatal (Courmayeur, 
<normalizedToken id="D8AB5E2BCA54C2BF191DA21F9561D153" originalValue="Crétaz" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">Cretaz</normalizedToken>
), 
<normalizedToken id="40DFEAB6C4DC16F81A3499747E8AA2A0" originalValue="östliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="554">oestliche</normalizedToken>
Bergamasker Alpen? (Clusone, Schilpario).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
